{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-03129/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-03129"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:31:29"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["plan américain"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["high"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["exterior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, tracking, crane, tilt"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man and woman walk on a hillside by the sea, holding hands."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-03129","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-03129"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/canvas/1/62f728ef-3240-49dc-88cf-de1be274f1af","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:52:31.986Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Ever meticulous, Daniel Day-Lewis helped choose much of Reynolds’s wardrobe, including wool and cashmere fabrics from the Savile Row tailors <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW249542584 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.anderson-sheppard.co.uk/\"><u>Anderson &amp; Sheppard</u></a> (Hirschberg, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW249542584 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.wmagazine.com/story/exclusive-daniel-day-lewis-giving-up-acting-phantom-thread\"><u>Daniel Day-Lewis Opens Up</u></a>”).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:747.1844660194175,493.3980582524272,369.70873786407753,388.3495145631068"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/canvas/1/1a2c21da-be4a-4cfc-b991-2c97230938a3","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:52:46.218Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>As the couple walk, hand in hand, across the hill, the sun rises before them, bathing them in new light. This represents both the beginning of their new relationship and the changes Alma will bring to Reynolds’s life. The sun is dawning on their partnership, so to speak, and Alma’s presence will bring a new beginning for the long-dead House of Woodcock, even if neither of them know it yet.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:96.31067961165051,53.78640776699026,438.0582524271845,278.05825242718447"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/canvas/1/1aa4ce32-53d9-42a5-9893-84044d3e26e1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:53:01.901Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>With Alma in his life, it’s as if Reynolds has stepped out from the window in the café where they met. <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW266710241 BCX4\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-01537.html\"><u>There</u></a>, she was associated with the outside world, and she seemed to represent an invitation to open up. Now the pair has reached that outside and more emotionally open space.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03129/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1245.8252427184466,80.19417475728153,375.9223300970873,408.5436893203884"}}}]}]}]}